$ Oracle wait event: log buffer space
@ log buffer space

The `log buffer space` event indicates that the session is waiting for the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/processes/background/LGWR[LGWR process] to make room in the → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/SGA/redo-log-buffer.
-
The more descriptive name is *log buffer full - LGWR bottleneck*

sa:

 `→ development/databases/Oracle/installed/dynamic-performance-views/event_name`
